Package: nimbleAPT
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Parallel Tempering for Nimble Models
Version: 1.0.3
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2020-19-08
Author: David Pleydell
Maintainer: David Pleydell <david.pleydell@inrae.fr>
Description: Functions for adaptive parallel tempering (APT) with nimble models. The adaptive parallel tempering algorithm is based on Misajedow's 2013 and 2016 papers. The package was previously released under the name nimble-snippets.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE | GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2),
    nimble,
    methods
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
